wiki.summary: “Good Luck, Babe!“ is a single released by Chappell Roan on April 5th, 2024. The song entails a relationship Chappell Roan had with a woman who struggled with compulsory heterosexuality, the conflict eventually causing their split. Roan teased this song a month prior to its release by sharing a minute-long snippet. Additionally, she further teased the track by performing it live before its initial release date. Read more on Last.fm.
